list.abstract: 《Qualified》是Dr. John演唱的歌曲，于2007年4月2日发行，收录于《Definitive Pop: Dr. John》专辑中。

yingyinNormal.en: I told you, Sid. You're not qualified to run a camp.
yingyinNormal.zh: 喜德，你没有经营营地的资格。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't hire an assistant because they're cute, you hire them because they're qualified.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别因为他长得帅就雇他当助理，你得考虑到他们的工作能力。

yingyinNormal.en: I like you, Kate. You're qualified, you're smart, and I need someone right now by my side.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我喜欢你，凯特。你能胜任，你很聪明。

yingyinNormal.en: He was up there because he's the only one qualified to install a piece of equipment that he designed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他上太空是因为他是唯一一个有资格安装他设计的设备的人。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, Joey has a very careful screening process. Apparently, not everyone is qualified to own wood and nails.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔伊有一套严格的筛选过程，并非每个人都适合拥有木制品。

yingyinNormal.en: Raj, don't dangle false hope in front of Leonard like that. Excuse me, but I think I'm just as qualified as you are.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拉杰，别在莱纳德面前乱说一些给他希望的话。抱歉，我跟你完全一样有资格，有希望，好吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Really? Well, there are others who might be more qualified, but the thought of interviewing them gave me a stomachache.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真的？的确有很多人比你们更加够格，但一想到要面试他们我就胃疼。

yingyinNormal.en: And you're clearly more than qualified for this job. You're actually, like, way overqualified, and we were so impressed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 并且您远远超越了这项符合工作的标准，你真的是远远超过了合格线，我们对你非常欣赏。

yingyinNormal.en: But aren't you interested in electronics? What about engineering? There's a growing market for qualified technicians. What about that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 但你不也对电子学感兴趣吗？转向工程方面怎么样？最近人才市场上训练有素的技术人员需求很旺，这个怎么样？

yingyinNormal.en: You're all wasting your time. Sheldon is the most qualified for the job, and no amount of gravity-defying bosom's going to change that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们都在浪费时间，谢尔顿最有资格获得这一职位，再大的反地心引力胸部也不能改变这一点。

yingyinNormal.en: Because you need us. Yes, the world is a vulnerable place, and yes, we helped make it that way. But we're also the ones best qualified to defend it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为你们需要我们。是的，这个世界是个脆弱的地方，没错，其中有我们的责任，但我们也是最有能力去保护她的人。

yingyinNormal.en: That's an impressive accomplishment. He's now an inspiration to millions of Americans who know you don't have to be special or even qualified to go into space.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那的确是一项令人赞叹的成就，他现在成功鼓舞了百万美国人，就算你不特别，甚至不够格，也都可以登上外太空。

yingyinNormal.en: No, there's three. You don't... you don't... I brought them into the world, Jack. I am perfectly qualified to sit here and watch them sleep and crap themselves for a couple of hours. Now go. Now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不了，他们三个呢，你不会……我亲手把他们带到这世上，杰克。我绝对有资格花几小时坐在这里看他们睡觉和拉屎。去睡吧，走吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Which is something I realized when I was viewing Earth from the deck of the International Space Station, where I spent two months as a payload specialist, a job I was qualified for because I'm an MIT-trained engineer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我意识到这点时是在遥远的外太空，当时我从国际空间站的甲板上瞭望地球，我以科学宇航员的身份待了两个月，这份工作我完全能胜任，因为我是麻省理工培养出来的工程师。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Increasing the number of opportunities for board membership without increasing the pool of <highlight>qualified</highlight> women has led to a "golden skirt" phenomenon.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 增加董事会成员的机会而不增加符合资格的女性人数导致了一种“金裙子”现象。

examination_example.sentence: It is in the best interest of a school to turn out graduates who are as <highlight>qualified</highlight> as possible.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 培养出尽可能合格的毕业生符合学校的最大利益。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Qualified</highlight> multilingual youngsters from other countries are proving to have a competitive advantage over their British counterparts.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 事实证明，来自其他国家的懂多种语言的合格年轻人比英国同龄人有竞争优势。
